User Story 1
---------------------
Nouns
- Air traffic controller
- Passenger
- Destination
- Airport
- Plane

Verbs
- Get
- Instruct
- Land
- Confirm



object      Message
------------------------
Plane       Land
Air Traffic  confirm, instruct


Air Traffic => instruct => plane <=> land <=> confirm

