User Story 3
-----------------------------

Nouns
- Air traffic controller
- weather
- (airplane)

Verbs
- ensure
- prevent
- takeoff


object      Message
-----------------------------
air traffic prevent
plane       takeoff


air traffic => weather(stormy) => prevent <=> takeoff <=> plane
              \weather(clear) => takeoff <=> plane


